data.description: Located in the Alta Mesa neighborhood, this oversized, cul-de-sac lot with no neighbors on one side or behind! 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with gorgeous laminate flooring, shutter blinds, and vaulted ceilings. Perfect for entertaining, there is a wet bar, built-in with cabinets in the living room. A cozy wood burning fireplace in the kitchen/dinging room area, with a charming bay window with bench seating, tons of storage and counter space and beautiful maple cabinetry. The backyard is an entertainers dream! With a large covered patio, beautiful sparkling pool with shade and an outdoor kitchen/bar top with space for a grill. Go see this right away!!
